text: Damjan Vtič (born 13 May 1985) is a Slovenian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Slovenia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Trebnje
